id: M. (Amegachile) —. Mandible with third tooth pointed or rounded, fourth tooth usually rather broad, rounded or truncate, rarely acute, rarely emarginate so that mandible ﬁve-toothed;  cutting edges not crenulate ........................M. (Paracella)
